			<div class="textwidget"><p><a title="About Luna &#038; Sol" href="https://lonerwolf.com/about/"><img  src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAP///wAAACwAAAAAAQABAEACAkQBADs=" data-lazy-src="https://cdn.lonerwolf.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/luna-sol-home-sidebar-1-min.jpg" alt="Luna &#038; Sol image" width="314" height="217" /><noscript><img  src="https://cdn.lonerwolf.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/luna-sol-home-sidebar-1-min.jpg" alt="Luna &#038; Sol image" width="314" height="217" /></noscript></a></p>
<p>Our names are Aletheia Luna and Mateo Sol. We&#8217;re <a title="Twin Flame" href="/twin-flame/"><strong>twin flames</strong></a>, spiritual mentors and soulwork teachers who currently live in Perth, Australia. </p>
<p>Our mission is to help you rediscover and reconnect with your soul through the practice of soulwork. We write about topics such as <a title="Spiritual Awakening" href="/spiritual-awakening/"><strong>spiritual awakening</strong></a>, discovering and channeling your gifts (such as those that <a title="empaths" href="/empath/"><strong>empaths</strong></a> have), thriving in loving relationships (like twin flames) and progressing as an <a title="Old Soul" href="/old-soul/"><strong>old soul</strong></a> in soulful maturation.</p>
<p>Find out more about <a title="Soulwork" href="/what-is-soulwork/"><strong>soulwork</strong></a>.</p>
